{"tid":1838853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議救護將接收到既武漢病人送去衛生署辦公室陳小姐間房到隔離14天？","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:30:29.000Z","uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a38c4dd1e7c5cf01286202ffa16eb3859e9a8db","tid":1838853,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，日日係間房都做野，根本就唔知而家出面既人既心情<br />\n<br />\n翻工放工都有專車接送，地鐵唔撚識搭，巴士唔撚識坐。叫做好防疫，一尾拖。<br />\n<br />\n如果班打工仔出事，真係多得你唔少！<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我極支持從武漢翻黎既病人，唔好去醫院隔離，去衛生署陳小姐間房隔離14天</span></span>"},{"pid":"52de61ee4dccc6d23000aa1d7d519b3d934999e6","tid":1838853,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，日日出口交文，但又唔知出面既人既心情，屌哪聲，專車接送唔洗同人逼車<br />\n<br />\n大陸人有走過武漢，有病都唔出聲，如果逼埋一架巴士同人放工你就係千古罪人。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果有去過武漢既人翻黎，去衛生署隔離就好了"},{"pid":"d58f522d47d44fe9367b18da9fc08b7b2f4b2723","tid":1838853,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"［行動］請文宣向有意到港醫病嘅武漢肺炎患者，引導佢地搵香港警署求助<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837289</a>"}]}